snippet.title: Ocean Planet - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Ocean Planet takes the essence of "Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy" and treats it as an art form, with atmospheric & immersive visuals and audio. You will be plunged into a diverse aquatic world, and it is up to you to rise up and see what awaits you at the surface.

🎮 Ocean Planet Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2985740/Ocean_Planet/
🌐 Ocean Planet Discord: https://discord.gg/23qxUNVS
